import React from 'react'; import { useLocation, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import { motion } from 'framer-motion'; const BookingConfirmation = () => { const location = useLocation(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const { bookingData, services, total } = location.state || {}; // If no booking data, redirect to services if (!bookingData || !services) { navigate('/services'); return null; } // Generate a random booking ID for display const bookingId = `HE${Date.now().toString().slice(-6)}`; return (
{/* Success Icon */}

Booking Confirmed!

Your service booking has been successfully confirmed. We'll contact you shortly.

{/* Booking Details */}

Booking Details

Booking ID: {bookingId}
Date: {new Date(bookingData.preferredDate).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { weekday: 'long', year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
Time: {bookingData.preferredTime}
Address: {bookingData.address}
Phone: {bookingData.phone}
{bookingData.notes && (
Special Instructions: {bookingData.notes}
)}
{/* Service Summary */}

Service Summary

{services.map((service, index) => (

{service.name}

{service.provider}

₹{service.price}

))}
{/* Total */}
Subtotal ₹{total}
Service Fee ₹50
Total Paid ₹{total + 50}
{/* What's Next Section */}

What's Next?

Confirmation Call

Our team will call you within 30 minutes to confirm the booking details.

Professional Assigned

A verified professional will be assigned to your booking within 2 hours.

Service Completed

Our professional will arrive on time and complete the service efficiently.

{/* Action Buttons */} {/* Contact Info */}

Need Help?

Our customer support team is here to help you 24/7

+91 9876543210
support@homeease.com
); }; export default BookingConfirmation;
